headline.main: North Korea to Expel Malaysian Envoy in Row Over Bizarre Airport Killing
headline.print_headline: North Korea to Expel Malaysian Envoy in Row Over Bizarre Airport Killing

lead_paragraph: North Korea said on Monday it has designated the Malaysian ambassador to the country as "persona non grata" and demanded the envoy leave the country within 48 hours from 10 a.m. on Sunday, its official KCNA news agency said.
